---
title: Sticky Falafels, Halloumi & Chermoula Veggies with Almond Salad
description: Make friends with plant-based ingredients by teaming hearty falafels with some stellar sides: chermoula roasted veggies, a
crunchy salad and a garlic dip so flavourful, you'll want to add it to everything.

